{"tid":1484382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2233 警方警告示威者立即離開金鐘一帶","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:18.000Z","uid":41404,"like":48,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1c37e1775a8bfe80201a3f38dfb2ee26f5d8e2","tid":1484382,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"警方警告示威者立即離開金鐘一帶<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  大批示威者現時仍佔據金鐘夏慤道行車線，嚴重影響附近一帶交通。示威者用丫叉將硬物投向政府總部，更用鐳射光線照射於政府總部佈防的警務人員，威脅在場各人的人身安全。警方警告示威者必須停止違法行為，立即離開。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月18日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時33分"},{"pid":"3df0b38889fc66db3a25c56756e2a9ccca6b0a39","tid":1484382,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/18/P2019081800828.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F18%2FP2019081800828.htm&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8mg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=27208fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/18/P2019081800828.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2b1ca47a6ae9975f23c40a97a49365201cdb3aed","tid":1484382,"uid":235465,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再唔散認真會出事"},{"pid":"327ae3a2a42a5a7a1b364cd14ddd9b89df6d9d7e","tid":1484382,"uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"返屋企!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b69b96afe7c40136693da3725a4407b81820bed","tid":1484382,"uid":191762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"返屋企啦"},{"pid":"537abc094841c4289ce5a330d2f5020dc224c82e","tid":1484382,"uid":290176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2b1ca47a6ae9975f23c40a97a49365201cd